item.description:
@davidude36 wrote:

I take the same stuff that pault takes ;)…
jokes, but i have 9 lessons in a day, well ill explain
we have 3 lessons in morning (40mins long each)
break (40mins)
3 more lessons (40 mins each)
lunch (40 mins)
2 more lessons (40 mins each)
break (40 mins)
3 more lessons (40 mins each)
my day starts around 8:30 or furthur, we finish at 5:20.
its a nice day, feels less then in my old school when we finished at 3:15

item.description:

Cheatest:

really how long is school there? 7 hours in united states 5 days a week

one subject here is 70 mins, i have two days with 5 subjects a day, and one with 4 subjects a day, include about 45 - 60 minutes break between it, and you have the time i go to school…

Cheatest:

wow… something there is lieing what school do you have 12 classes…

fyi: im on vwo(voorbereidend wetenschappelijk onderwijs, in english: preparing scientific education or something), it’s the highest you can get ona dutch highschool.
but all grades in highschools have like 12 - 13 subjects until you’re in the second phase, you get to choose the subjects you want, even though you have some subjects you’re forced to take
